Frequently Asked Questions

When and where does Musikfest Wannsee take place?

Musikfest Wannsee takes place from June 15-20, 2025, at various venues around the Wannsee area in Berlin, Germany.

What types of music will be performed?

The festival features a diverse range of musical styles, including classical, contemporary, jazz, opera, and folk music. Check our program page for details on specific performances.

Is the festival suitable for children?

Yes, we have several family-friendly events, including a dedicated Children's Concert. Children under 12 receive discounted tickets for most events.
